  ],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "Part I:  Authorizes the construction and occupation of self-contained relocatable housing units, with certain restrictions.  Part II:  Specifies that a manufactured home is considered real property, requiring its transfer, conveyance, and mortgage to follow the same recording and enforcement requirements as other real property.  Effective 7/1/3000.  (HD3)"
    }
  ],
